{
  "stem": "23599.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a big like a-- a really small one room for garbage, for stuff to throw away or to put away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had to move in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to move in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when there was a aussiedlung, when they had the people, everybody, it was usually they called everybody that lived there to be on the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they were taking-- they were taking away mostly there was time where they took old people or workers, depending, younger ones or so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a young couple with a little girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so anyhow, everybody had to go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they couldn't-- the husband couldn't go down because he broke his leg, and he couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he stayed there in that room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she and the girl went back and went out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when she came back with the girl, the man was still in bed, but he was shot dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the police came and checked out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they saw the guy in bed, and he was supposed to be outside so they shot him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did people react to what was going on?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to accept it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to accept it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do we have to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't accept it, they will shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we tried to get away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, no, not really personally I saw it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were lots of things which we heard about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and there was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but you-- we tried to stay away from all those things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what to tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was important to have a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So actually I got a job then, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
